data.name: Label1.Text
data.value: As a passionate lover of fashion, I realized there was a gap in the market for affordable yet stylish clothing that makes every woman feel her best. After years of dreaming about opening my own boutique, I decided to take the leap and launch For Women by Me. It’s a boutique that’s not just about selling clothes—it’s about helping women embrace their individuality and feel empowered by their style.
